                                       "可选 vital/self/day/terrain/plants/animals/resources/inventory/shelter/water/threat/biome/lastact/spatial/nutrition/weather"},
             "seed": {"type": "integer", "description": "固定 seed(默认 12345,保证各 stage 重放同一批世界可对照)"},
